- Current bot supports /start, /me, text handling, callback handling, and low-level interactions audit logging
- The product is evolving from a single-user training bot into a teacher-student learning product
- This feature is non-trivial and must be implemented through the agent workflow
- New feature logic should be introduced in focused modules where appropriate
- New feature is not complete without tests

